---
title: 'Contact'
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 text-black dark:text-white p-8 rounded shadow-md w-full max-w-3xl mx-auto transition-colors duration-300">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Contacto</h1>
    <p class="mb-4 text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
      ¿Tienes alguna pregunta o quieres trabajar conmigo? Completa el formulario y te responderé lo antes posible.
    </p>
    
    <form class="space-y-6">
      <div>
        <label class="block text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 mb-2">Nombre</label>
        <input type="text" class="w-full p-3 rounded bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 text-black dark:text-white border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-400" placeholder="Tu nombre">
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <label class="block text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 mb-2">Correo Electrónico</label>
        <input type="email" class="w-full p-3 rounded bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 text-black dark:text-white border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-400" placeholder="tucorreo@example.com">
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <label class="block text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 mb-2">Mensaje</label>
        <textarea class="w-full p-3 rounded bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 text-black dark:text-white border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-400" placeholder="Escribe tu mensaje aquí"></textarea>
      </div>

      <button type="submit" class="bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition">
        Enviar Mensaje
      </button>
    </form>
  </section>
</Layout>